# AI Pipeline Rules

The pipeline is deterministic.

Every stage

has one responsibility.

Every stage

produces artifacts.

Every stage

can resume.

Every stage

can retry.

Stages

Validate

↓

Fingerprint

↓

Extract Audio

↓

Speech Recognition

↓

Transcript

↓

Translation

↓

Speech

↓

Mux

↓

Verification

Never skip validation.

Never modify previous artifacts.

Never delete artifacts.

Use cache whenever possible.

Translation and speech generation

may execute in parallel.

Muxing never runs in parallel.
